{"tid":2267472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GFRIEND線上開唱！轉身見「粉絲隔空應援」全員淚崩","createTime":"2020-11-02T05:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T11:42:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8af0c3920ba7e188bd78bbc6d6bbb4e915b827","tid":2267472,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:59:38.000Z","msg":"南韓女團GFriend昨（31）天下午舉辦首次線上演唱會，這也是她們自從去年11月結束亞巡最後一站，在日本橫濱的演唱會後，時隔將近1年再度站上舞台與粉絲們見面，6位成員皆表示相當激動，昨天正好是萬聖節，她們也應景地準備了變裝舞台，為全世界的歌迷們帶來將近90分鐘的精彩表演。<br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND以〈Labyrinth〉和〈FINGERTIP〉揭開演唱會的序幕，緊接著是〈Rough〉、〈NAVILLERA〉、〈Glass Bead〉、〈Me Gustas Tu〉等多首代表作，成員們說「回首過往，覺得比起以前更加自在了，跟粉絲間的距離越來越近，希望未來也能一起創造更多的回憶」。之後她們便在不同部位畫上流血特效妝，演唱〈APPLE〉，還公開了新專輯中不同風格的3組小分隊舞台。<br />\n<br />\n活動接近尾聲，她們也感嘆說「越表演到後面，越能夠感受到粉絲的空缺，希望可以親自面到面，互相聽到對方聲音表演的那天能夠趕快到來」，而最後一首歌〈Crossroads〉結束後，出現了粉絲們提前寄來信整理成的VCR，讓6姝相當感動，最後安可，表演〈Here We Are〉時，看到後方大螢幕上的Buddy們（官方粉絲名）紛紛拿起應援棒隔空應援，讓她們忍不住淚灑舞台，大喊「真的很想念大家，謝謝你們」。<br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND第三張韓語正規專輯《回：Walpurgis Night》將在11月9日發行。"},{"pid":"ab6c100d2d90b903839bd39d58b5b0311e41e2e5","tid":2267472,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2857166-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2857166-PH.jpg&h=51f800ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND昨（31）天下午舉辦首次線上演唱會。（圖／iME提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2857161-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2857161-PH.jpg&h=78c3156d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲睿隣、信飛帶來〈Secret Diary〉。（圖／iME提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2857162-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2857162-PH.jpg&h=e121736c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲所願、嚴智帶來〈Better Me〉。（圖／iME提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2857163-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2857163-PH.jpg&h=20afacac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲裕株、銀河帶來〈Night Drive〉。（圖／iME提供）"},{"pid":"2fb7d699775c6be0fb5666d3541d95af640acbf4","tid":2267472,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/01/2857164-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2F2857164-PH.jpg&h=0994b92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND看到粉絲們拿著應援棒隔空應援，忍不住留下淚來。 （圖／iME提供）"},{"pid":"13dc31b0811ca686326248ff46d0b71bda5a4078","tid":2267472,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"人面全非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1320083a78f7a07bad07e06fc6c08f506fae5e1a","tid":2267472,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a471a75a362ca2c7f4358c3b0c0364df805f36","tid":2267472,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13dc31b0811ca686326248ff46d0b71bda5a4078","tid":2267472,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"人面全非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i2.tcafe2a.com/2010/20201027152931_fb86029b4427b6ae2c4edc1d5408a388_d0cs.gif\" data-t